sql:
SELECT name
FROM meteorites
WHERE mass = (SELECT MAX(mass) FROM meteorites);

external_knowledge:
This query does not require any external knowledge to interpret the results; 
The query result is a list of meteorite names; 
The names are ordered alphabetically for easier reference.

sql:
SELECT name
FROM meteorites
ORDER BY name;

